<td style=" color:#000000; font-size:12pt; background-color:#FFFFFF; font-family:arial; bLabel:main; bEditID:r3st1;" tEditID="c1r1" locked="0" aEditID="c1r1" >
<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; text-align: right; font-family: arial; "><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000066" size="6">British International School</font></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; text-align: right; font-family: arial; "><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000066" size="6">Kuala Lumpur</font></span></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" size="4"><i>Part of The British Schools <font size="4">Founda<font size="4">t<font size="4">ion</font></font></font><br></i></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#c0c0c0" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="6"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" size="1"><i><br></i></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left; "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="-webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 5px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 5px; "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left; "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="-webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 5px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 5px; "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation}&nbsp;{!Contact.FirstName}&nbsp;{!Contact.LastName},</font></span></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; text-align: right; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="-webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 5px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 5px;"></span></font></div><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; " lang="en-GB"><div style="margin:0;"><font face="Calibri,sans-serif" size="2"><span style="font-size:11pt;"><font color="#002060" size="3"><span style="font-size:12pt;"><br><font color="#000000" face="Arial,Sans-Serif" size="3">There has been a case of head lice or nits in foundation school. Therefore, your child might have been exposed.&nbsp; Children may also be exposed in places other than schools such as children activities centres and visiting or spending the night in other children’s homes.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br><br>It is recommended that you check your child daily for signs of lice for the next week as indicated below:<br>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Using very good lighting (bright sun or lamp), search your child’s hair for live lice and/or nits (lice eggs).<br>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Part the hair many times and look behind the ears, on the crown of the head, and the back of the neck.&nbsp; <br>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Lice are about the size of a sesame seed and can be light tan to dark brown.&nbsp; They move quickly through the hair.<br>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Nits are attached directly to the hair shaft.&nbsp; They look like a grain of salt and are hard to remove.&nbsp; <br><br>Treatment for head lice requires the use of medicated anti-lice shampoo that can be purchased at pharmacies or clinics.<br>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Keep your child away from school until he/she has been properly treated.<br>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Apply the shampoo, according to package instructions.<br>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Do not a conditioner before using lice shampoo.&nbsp; Do not re-wash hair for 1-2 days.<br>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Use a fine-tooth nit comb to remove any lice or nits from hair after shampooing.<br>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; After treatment, checking the hair and combing with a nit comb to remove nits every 2-3 days may decrease the chance of reinfestation.<br>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Retreatment in recommended after 1 week in order to kill any surviving hatched lice before they produce new eggs.<br>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Practice good hand washing.<br>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bed linen, hats, cushions, comb etc will need to be thoroughly washed in hot soapy water. The use of clothes dryer on the hottest settings is also useful.<br>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Do not allow the sharing of hairbrushes, combs, hats etc between family members and friends.<br>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Students with long hair should keep it tied back.<br><br>If you are unsure of what to look for or do, please don’t hesitate to contact us at the school by emailing the school nurse at azilah.chan@britishschool.edu.my. Thank you for your attention to this matter.<br><br>Azilah Chan<br>School Nurse</font><br></span></font></span></font><span lang="EN-GB"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><font class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 32, 96); font-size: medium; " size="3"><o:p></o:p></font></font></span></div></span><font class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; " face="Arial, sans-serif"> </font><font style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; " size="3"><span style="font-family: Arial,Sans-Serif;"><br><font size="3">Regards,</font><br></span></font><font class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; " face="arial"><span lang="en-GB"></span></font><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">Administration Team</font><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: left; "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">The British International School of Kuala Lumpur</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: left; "><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; "><i><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600"><b>World Class Education</b></font></i></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: left; "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: left; "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">__________________________________________________________</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center; "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">Beijing - Kuala Lumpur - Sao Paulo - Manila - Moscow - Guangzhou - Nanjing - Tashkent - Pamplona - Marbella</font></div>]]></td>
